private static final JsonObject KNOWN_JSON = JsonFactory.newObjectBuilder()
            .set(PolicyCommand.JsonFields.TYPE, ModifySubject.TYPE)
            .set(PolicyCommand.JsonFields.JSON_POLICY_ID, TestConstants.Policy.POLICY_ID.toString())
            .set(ModifySubject.JSON_LABEL, TestConstants.Policy.LABEL.toString())
            .set(ModifySubject.JSON_SUBJECT_ID, TestConstants.Policy.SUBJECT.getId().toString())
            .set(ModifySubject.JSON_SUBJECT, TestConstants.Policy.SUBJECT.toJson(FieldType.regularOrSpecial()))
            .build();
public static final String TYPE = TYPE_PREFIX + NAME;

static final JsonFieldDefinition<String> JSON_LABEL =
            JsonFactory.newStringFieldDefinition("label", FieldType.REGULAR, JsonSchemaVersion.V_2);

static final JsonFieldDefinition<String> JSON_SUBJECT_ID =
            JsonFactory.newStringFieldDefinition("subjectId", FieldType.REGULAR, JsonSchemaVersion.V_2);

static final JsonFieldDefinition<JsonObject> JSON_SUBJECT =
            JsonFactory.newJsonObjectFieldDefinition("subject", FieldType.REGULAR, JsonSchemaVersion.V_2);
